Karen Greenlee made national headlines in the mid-80's when she drove off in a hearse and wasn't heard from for two days. Many other strange events took place around this time, notably the disappearence of her name sake and friend, Karen Davis, who was never found. She was interviewed in the book [[Apocalypse Culture]]. The excerpt [http://www.nokilli.com/sacto/karen-greenlee.htm "The Unrepentant Necrophile]: An Interview with Karen Greenlee" is available online.
